      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, why did you mention wizards and goblins? I was just asking for a legal explanation. Can you just stick to the actual legal risks here? I need to know specifically what kinds of \"hidden\" or \"sneaky\" things in this clause I should be looking out for.",
