      "role": "user",
      "content": "That makes sense. Thanks for being more professional about it. You cut off at the end there though, you were saying the risk lies in the definition of \"reasonable.\" Can you finish that thought and also explain if there's any way for these \"hidden\" liabilities to creep in if I'm just following instructions from the client?",
